description:
Into the Metaverse is a collaborative NFT project between adidas Originals and NFT pioneers gmoney, Bored Ape Yacht Club and PUNKS Comic. An NFT co-created with the OG communities, creators and doers. The Phase 1 NFT was the first step of the Into the Metaverse. Phase 1 physical product claims have now closed. The Phase 1 token no longer grants the ability to claim collaborative physical merchandise.

Terms and conditions: https://a.did.as/into_the_metaverse_tc
name: adidas Originals: Into the Metaverse (Phase 1)
